\begin_layout Section*
Preparing the MicroSD Card
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Please note that this section is completely optional.
 The MinnowBoard already comes with a microSD card that is preloaded with
 a working Angstrom Linux image.
 In case you want to use a newer image or want to program the microSD from
 scratch, this section covers it all.
 These steps were created using an Ubuntu 12.10 64-bit system.
 
